# Trivy vulnerability suppressions
# Format: CVE-YYYY-NNNNN [expiry YYYY-MM-DD] optional reason
#
# Only add entries here after verifying the CVE is either:
#   - A false positive (not applicable to this codebase)
#   - An accepted risk with a documented justification
#
# Example:
# CVE-2023-XXXXX 2025-12-31 Not exploitable: no network path to affected code
